 Photo: Instagram Priyanka Chopra has disclosed that she has been spending more time at home since the birth of her baby with Nick Jonas  via surrogacy.   The former beauty queen who hosted a pre Oscar event on Wednesday, where South Asian artists’ were recognised made this known at the event. Chorpa, delivered a speech where she couldn’t help but mention her parenting experience thus far. “Haven’t been stepping out anywhere but had to come here tonight just to say this that I’m highly proud to be rubbing shoulders with all of you and encouraging you.”  